reviewText: I have not watched this DVD yet but I know its going to be good.
Not bad. Pretty interesting behind the scene stuff in here. :=)
I love the UFC. But, this didn't measure up to my standards.
My husband watches this stuff and he seemed to like the DVD just fine.  He's watched it a few times.  The shipping was quick and it was a pleasant shopping experience.
This is recommended for someone who likes man's drama behind the scene rather than fighting scene. funny and furious.

The stuff I usually order from here are text books for my son who I home school.  He is very interested in Ultimate Fighting so in some of his down time his friends and him watch this.  They love it!  They watch it a lot.
